* `C-c C-f C-f` : +fold/toggle
* `C-c C-f C-a C-f` : +fold/close-all
* `C-c C-f C-u` : +fold/open
* `C-c C-f C-a C-u` : +fold/open-all
* `C-c M-g` : magit-file-dispatch
* `M-x` : execute-extended-command
* `C-c override-state` : all
